{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e4cfe833a0","title":"在中共中央政治局常委会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cdcb4ff3f6","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":27,"articleId":"e4cfe833a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"598ab4f5b0","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局常委会议上的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"},{"id":"3fc4a2f719","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月27日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"},{"id":"dae55db711","type":"paragraph","text":"部队减员，队伍虽小，但它是将来发展的基础。现在环境改变，二万里完结，将来再不会有二万里，应向干部解释发展前途。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"},{"id":"f26bb2088f","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五、二十六军在甘泉、富县集中配合作战。如能再对杨虎城、孙蔚如由南城开清水的一路继续给予打击，能打两个胜仗，即可打破“围”。要在严冬之前粉碎敌人“围期”","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"},{"id":"52eb201959","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在中共中央政治局常委会议上关于部队工作和关于陕甘支队南下与红二十五、二十六军会合粉碎国民党军的“围”问题讲话的一部分。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"},{"id":"b721601109","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]杨虎城，当时任国民党军第十七路军总指挥、西安绥靖公署主任。孙蔚如，当时任国民党军第三十八军军长。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0"}],"page":{"id":"86f14c2713","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"e4cfe833a0","start":255,"end":255}}}},"__N_SSG":true}